\item Card 1 has four matching numbers, so you win one copy each of the
next four cards: cards 2, 3, 4, and 5.
\item Your original card 2 has two matching numbers, so you win one copy
each of cards 3 and 4.
\item Your copy of card 2 also wins one copy each of cards 3 and 4.
\item Your four instances of card 3 (one original and three copies) have
