one matching number, so you win \emph{eight} copies of card 5.
\item Your fourteen instances of card 5 (one original and thirteen copies)
have no matching numbers and win no more cards.
\item Your one instance of card 6 (one original) has no matching numbers
and wins no more cards.
}

